---
// Roadmap section — 4-phase timeline
---

<section id="roadmap">
  <div class="section-inner">

    <!-- Section heading -->
    <h2 class="roadmap-heading" data-reveal="fade">
      Roadmap
      <svg class="roadmap-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z"></path>
        <line x1="4" y1="22" x2="4" y2="15"></line>
      </svg>
    </h2>

    <!-- Intro paragraph -->
    <p class="roadmap-intro" data-reveal="fade">
      Rosie's Heroes is developing a scalable, data-backed sterilization and vaccination program in
      high-rabies countries, starting in India. The vision is simple but ambitious: drive sustained
      70%+ coverage in targeted districts until rabies transmission collapses entirely.
    </p>

    <!-- Timeline: zigzag layout with centre vertical line -->
    <div class="roadmap-timeline">

      <!-- Top dot -->
      <div class="timeline-dot" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;"></div>

      <!-- Phase 1 — left side -->
      <div class="phase phase--left-col" data-reveal="card">
        <h4 class="phase-title">
          <span class="gold">Phase 1:</span> Target Identification
        </h4>
        <p class="phase-body">
          Map high-burden districts. Establish local partnerships and define coverage baselines.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 2 — right side -->
      <div class="phase phase--right-col" data-reveal="card">
        <h4 class="phase-title">
          <span class="gold">Phase 2:</span> High-Volume Operations
        </h4>
        <p class="phase-body">
          Deploy mobile sterilization and vaccination units. Track sterilization progress.
          Build community awareness and support networks.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 3 — left side -->
      <div class="phase phase--left-col" data-reveal="card">
        <h4 class="phase-title">
          <span class="gold">Phase 3:</span> Coverage Monitoring
        </h4>
        <p class="phase-body">
          Maintain and verify 70%+ coverage rates. Identify and address gaps.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 4 — right side -->
      <div class="phase phase--right-col" data-reveal="card">
        <h4 class="phase-title">
          <span class="gold">Phase 4:</span> Transmission Collapse
        </h4>
        <p class="phase-body">
          Sustained coverage drives rabies transmission to zero in targeted districts.
          Replicate to additional high-burden zones and countries.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Bottom dot -->
      <div class="timeline-dot" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;"></div>

    </div><!-- /.roadmap-timeline -->

  </div>

  <!-- Golden retriever — absolutely positioned at bottom-left -->
  <img
    id="howling-golden"
    src="/images/illus-golden-howling.png"
    alt="Howling golden retriever"
    loading="lazy"
    width="265"
    height="263"
  />
</section>

<style>
  #roadmap {
    background-color: var(--color-cream-story);
    padding: var(--space-20) 0 var(--space-25);
    position: relative;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  /* ---- Heading ---- */
  .roadmap-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-section);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-snug);
    line-height: var(--lh-tight);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .roadmap-icon {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ---- Intro ---- */
  .roadmap-intro {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: var(--lh-relaxed);
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-15);
  }

  /* ---- Timeline single-column layout ---- */
  .roadmap-timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Continuous vertical black line */
  .roadmap-timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  /* ---- Dots ---- */
  .timeline-dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    z-index: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* Animation is applied globally via #howling-golden in global.css */
  #howling-golden {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 250px;
    height: auto;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    #howling-golden {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  /* ---- Individual phase blocks ---- */
  .phase {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-5) 0;
  }

  /* Left-column phases: text on left half, right-aligned, connector goes right to centre */
  .phase--left-col {
    align-items: flex-end;
    text-align: right;
    padding-right: calc(50% + 45px); /* text stays left of centre + gap */
  }

  .phase--left-col::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    right: calc(50% - 1px);
    width: 30px;
    height: 2px;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
  }

  /* Right-column phases: text on right half, left-aligned, connector goes left to centre */
  .phase--right-col {
    align-items: flex-start;
    text-align: left;
    padding-left: calc(50% + 45px); /* text stays right of centre + gap */
  }

  .phase--right-col::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: calc(50% - 1px);
    width: 30px;
    height: 2px;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
  }

  .phase-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: var(--lh-snug);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .phase-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: var(--lh-relaxed);
  }

  /* Gold phase label */
  .gold {
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }
</style>
